Titolo: A Dark Room

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: A Dark Room is an open-source text-based role-playing game. It was originally published for web browsers by Canadian indie studio Doublespeak Games on June 10, 2013. Later that year, it was released in the App Store for iOS devices. In 2014, a prequel, The Ensign, was released for iOS and provided more insight into the world and its characters. An Android version was released in 2016. A Nintendo Switch version was released on April 12, 2019, but was temporarily removed from the Nintendo eShop shortly afterwards.

Genere: Online text-based role-playing game

Valutazione: 77
